Summary: Early AM, fluffy clouds with clear areas off to the west (back lighting sun). UFO floated between clouds.s
divs: Sighting DetailsI glanced at the sky to the west and saw a bright object floating between clouds. It was very shiny as the sun reflected its light off it, I viewed the UFO for about 30 seconds until the clouds obscured it.The UFO was viewed from the side (profile)and appeared cigar shaped.
